{"tid":1731172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋同我打好過心理戰!!","createTime":"2019-11-17T16:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T16:36:35.000Z","uid":240775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"569a0b393957b85f2e59ccccf3e48ab53c305f28","tid":1731172,"uid":240775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"小弟見到前線好多好勇敢嘅義士，但係有時都見到有啲喊晒口手震震嘅師兄。我明白大家好撚驚我自己都好驚但係唔可以俾情緒影響到呢場運動所以我決定要寫呢個post<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個post俾晒所有前線和你非同埋會去發夢嘅人睇；尤其是係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>Poly</ins></span>嘅人!!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>發夢做咩最緊要係個心理</ins></strong>；心理影響一切態度, 自信心同勇氣。每個人嘅心理都唔同所以小心自己講同做嘅嘢，你自己唔覺得但係係會影響到其他人：<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">要喊就細聲喊、要寫遺書就自己一個人寫唔好俾其他人見到、唔好講咩死啦我好驚比人塔啊</span></span></strong>；相反要做嘅就係鼓勵大家，同你身邊嘅義士鼓起勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">班狗開咪講咩點樣慫恿你哋點樣侮辱你哋除咗屌返佢之外，<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">高叫口號<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>光復香港時代革命</em></span>唔單止鼓起到大家嘅勇氣仲可以令對家心亂，再好玩啲嘅<span style=\"color: pink;\">係前線防守到大聲播<span style=\"color: gold;\">國歌</span>，狂replay</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要大聲到班狗都聽到!</span> 可以一齊唱，穩定吓驚嘅義士。</span></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n播下依啲歌都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3AUprJLA7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv3AUprJLA7w&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=bae047d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v3AUprJLA7w</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SEgjlxz7VT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSEgjlxz7VT8&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=9e1f5788\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SEgjlxz7VT8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ryqGOGig_AI\" data-sr-u